pipeline_summary.name: wait_for_file_pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Sensorgated pipeline that monitors daily transaction file arrivals, validates the file schema, and loads the data into a PostgreSQL table. The workflow is linear: a FileSensor gates the process, followed by a Pythonbased schema validation and a Pythonbased load to PostgreSQL.

components.name: Wait for Transaction File
components.description: Monitors the local filesystem for the daily transaction CSV file and emits a signal when the file is present.

connections.purpose: Local filesystem path for incoming transaction files

components.name: Validate Transaction File Schema
components.description: Checks that the transaction CSV file contains the required columns with correct data types.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the file arrival sensor succeeds

connections.purpose: Local filesystem path for incoming transaction files

components.name: Load Transactions into PostgreSQL
components.description: Loads the validated transaction data from the CSV file into the PostgreSQL table public.transactions.
